				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1918720&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205500" alt="Scorpion451" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1918720)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;" >Scorpion451</a></span> <span class="odate time_1470876147 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Aug 2016 00:42</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2555323">
									

<p>Looking at it in terms of pure counts and individual 𝚫's is actually kind of interesting:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Numb3rs&nbsp;R&nbsp;F∐n!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">And&nbsp;I&nbsp;am&nbsp;a&nbsp;total&nbsp;nerd:</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
