<p>🎺🎺🎺</p>
<p>On topic, I'd like to echo the sentiments of those requesting SCP object names on their pages, &lt; Prev | Next &gt; buttons, and SCP-# tags for tales including SCPs. These are easily accomplished and would have a positive impact on the ability to view and digest content. SCP names are often a hint at the idea that inspired the object, such as the Living Room. Navigation buttons on pages would bring people through the list sequentially, instead of just going down the list and clicking whichever SCP names seem interesting. SCP-# tags are nice for when an author is trying to vaguely reference an object that will no doubt get called out in the Discuss page anyway.</p>

							</div>

								
					
